description: The spider, with the long arms and legs, that wrap you up, and make you helpless. The Ninja, sneaky, quiet, calculating. A hard fought and grueling match between two warriors. Round 4 had to be canceled, so that is why we are giving this as an EXTRA update. Enjoy the match it was a great one.
title: The Spider (1-1) vs. The Ninja (3-0)
